ockquote><br />\n死就一定醒<br />\n但生命盡頭前有咩心願未了係一個遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997e664c769f0480ab12604af8ff6b98c660c650","tid":87614,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我人愈大心態愈年輕。</blockquote><br />\n我都希望可以咁<br />\n但人年紀越大就煩嘅野越多<br />\n好想回到讀書果時無憂無慮嘅學生生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2482199f6ac6e8f9d970e280363ea8327e27f2c2","tid":87614,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"好驚轉個撚頭三十歲 重唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申今年20 唔知做緊乜"},{"pid":"e90cfe3ff3b913c113c623234bd9a2fc6780628f","tid":87614,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好驚轉個撚頭三十歲 重唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申今年20 唔知做緊乜</blockquote><br />\n喺香港生活幾十年都係做緊奴隸<br />\n生活慘過奴隸<br />\n到死時你仲慘過奴隸<br />\n奴隸至省可以入土為安<br />\n我地死後d骨灰應該都係曬落海架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}